  "abstract": "ICGL 6 was isolated from a normal-leaved groundnut genotype OG 66-6-1 belonging to\r\nArachis hypogaea subsp. fastigiata var. vulgaris. A single plant with abnormally puckered\r\nleaves was observed in a population of OG 66-6-1 grown in the 1979/80 postrainy season at\r\nICRISAT Center. The plant was harvested and progeny rowed. Subsequently plants with\r\npuckered leaves were reselected in successive selfed generations, until their leaf phenotype\r\nwas stabilized.",
